data.description: GREEN CERTIFIED with a BONUS ROOM! This custom built newly constructed energy efficient home is located in the Pecan Meadows subdivision in Durant and has stunning upgrades to include Solar-panels, privacy fence, upgraded electric both in the panels and outlets. Electric bill averages $120monthly, that’s incredible! Situated on just over a half acre, you have plenty of space to spread out and enjoy the outdoors all enclosed by a wooden privacy fence. Gorgeous backyard vibes with a covered patio that is perfect for entertaining. Step inside to a beautiful gas fire place, large windows and an open concept with modern farmhouse vibes. Home is equipped with granite countertops throughout as well as great storage and a beautiful color scheme. Seller is leaving ALL gorgeous appliances including refrigerator! Home comes with newer washer/dryer, the laundry room also includes a sink and cabinets with granite countertops. In the backyard you’ll find a brand new storm shelter installed All Nestled on a quiet street with a beautiful country setting.
